A ''Sucker Punch'' is an act of violence where the one being punched is either caught completely and unexpectedly off guard by a landed fist, or a punch which is thrown to disable another in a place which is not normally a target in a "fair fight," such as on the back of the head (also known as a 'rabbit punch'). Although it is an embarassment and painful to be upon the receiving end of the punch, the act often belies the chatracter of the one throwing the punch, which is often attributed as a cowardly act.